title: Book of Beret 3
author: Elioto8
pages:
#- The book of Beret

Honor in working
#-  To you who do not spread the word, feel not regret, but pride. You, while not spreading his word, can help fuel his kingdom. You who farm, you feed the men and women that protect us and spread the word. You who build great structures, make them in his name, and be valiant in your
#- creations. You who master the art of battle and fight his wars, protect his name and follow his law. All who serve him shall follow his law and they who help interpret and enforce it. Listen to your governments, but also follow his rule. If man tries to restrict your belief in him, leave them and 
#- find safe harbor in another land. Even when you do not work, honor him by wearing a red leather helm.
#- 